videos.description: Colorado's Josh Fortune makes a two handed dunk to jump start the Buffalo's offense.
videos.headline: Colorado jumps out early with a strong dunk

videos.description: Arizona's Parker Jackson-Cartwright steals it from Colorado's Deleon Brown, and the Wildcats' Jackson-Cartwright connects with Rawle Alkins who makes the contested layup.
videos.headline: Arizona turns defense into offense with layup

videos.description: Arizona's Chance Comanche keeps the ball in play and finds Rawle Alkins for the 3 pointer.
videos.headline: Arizona keeps the ball in bounds and hits a 3

videos.description: Colorado's Wesley Gordon draws contact as he drives to the rim converting on the and-1.
videos.headline: Colorado's Gordon makes the contested layup for the and-1

videos.description: Arizona's Rawle Alkins denies Colorado's Bryce Peters under the rim.
videos.headline: Arizona's defense with the denial

videos.description: Colorado's George King misses the open layup in transition, but is there for the second attempt.
videos.headline: Colorado's King gets denied by the rim on the layup

videos.description: Colorado's Xavier Johnson has ice in his veins as he hits a jumper, down single digits. Arizona's Dusan Ristic answers with his own basket.
videos.headline: Colorado and Arizona swap jumpers

videos.description: Arizona's Lauri Markkanen misses a sure dunk.
videos.headline: Arizona's Markkanen misses easy dunk
